INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209103423', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>C语言规定:在一个源程序中.main函数的位置。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">必须在最开始</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">必须在系统调用的库函数的后面</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">可以任意</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">必须在最后</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-09 21:01:56');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209113419', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下叙述正确的是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">在C程序中,main函数必须位于程序的最前面</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">C程序的每行中只能写一条语句</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">C语言本身没有输入输出语句</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">在对一个C程序进行编译的过程中,可发现注释中的拼写错误</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-09 21:01:47');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209123407', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>一个C程序的执行是从（&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;）。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">本程序的main函数开始,到main函数结束</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">本程序文件的第一个函数开始,到本程序文件的最后一个函数结束</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">本程序的main函数开始,到本程序文件的最后一个函数结束</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">本程序文件的第一个函数开始,到本程序main函数结束</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-09 21:01:34');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209213338', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下叙述不正确的是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">一个C源程序可由一个或多个函数组成</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">一个C源程序必须包含一个main函数</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">C程序的基本组成单位是函数</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">在C程序中,注释说明只能位于一条语句的后面</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-14 14:17:28');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209213649', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>在C语言中(以16位PC机为例)，5种基本数据类型的存储空间长度的排列顺序为。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">char < int < longint <＝ float < double</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">char ＝ int < longint <＝ float < double</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">char < int < longint ＝ float ＝ double</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">char ＝ int ＝ longint <＝ float < double</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-09 22:39:53');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209213724', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>若x、i、j和k都是int型变量，则执行下面表达式后x的值为。</p><p>x＝(i＝4，j＝16，k＝32)</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">4</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">16</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">32</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">52</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-09 21:37:24');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209213801', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>假设所有变量均为整型，则表达式(a＝2,b＝5,b＋＋,a＋b)的值是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">7</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">8</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">6</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">2</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-09 21:38:01');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209214137', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>下列四组选项中，均不是C语言关键字的选项是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">define，IF，Type</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">getc，char，printf</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">include，scanf，case</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">while，go，pow</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-09 21:41:37');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209215524', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>下面四个选项中,均是C语言关键字的选项是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">auto，enum，include</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">switch，type，continue</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">signed，define，scanf</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if，struct，type</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-09 21:55:24');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209215608', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>C语言中的标识符只能由字母、数字和下划线三种字符组成，且第一个</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">必须为字母</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">必须为下划线</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">必须为字母或下划线</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">可以是字母、数字和下划线中任一种字符</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-09 21:56:08');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209215707', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>下面四个选项中,均是合法转义字符的选项是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">‘\\’’‘\\\\’‘\\n’</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">‘\\’‘\\017’‘\\”’</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">\\018’‘\\f’‘xab’</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">‘\\\\0’‘\\101’‘x1f’</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-09 21:57:07');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209215748', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>下面正确的字符常量是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">“c”</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">‘\\’’</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">‘W’</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">‘’</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-09 21:57:48');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209215816', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>下面不正确的字符串常量是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">‘abc’</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">“12\'12”</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">“0”</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">“”</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-09 21:58:16');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209220155', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>若有代数式<img class=\"fr-fin\" data-fr-image-preview=\"false\" alt=\"Image title\" src=\"img/q_img/20190211213647uploadq1.png\" width=\"32\">，则不正确的C语言表达式是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">a/b/c*e*3</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">3*a*e/b/c</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">3*a*e/b*c</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">a*e/c/b*3</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-11 21:36:50');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209220427', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>已知各变量的类型说明如下:</p><p>int k , a , b ;<br>unsigned long w ＝ 5 ;</p><p>double x ＝ 1.42 ;</p><p>则以下不符合C语言语法的表达式是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x%(－3)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">w＋＝－2</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">k＝(a＝2,b＝3,a＋b)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">a＋＝a－＝(b＝4)*(a＝3)</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-09 22:04:27');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209220503', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下不正确的叙述是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">在C程序中,逗号运算符的优先级最低</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">在C程序中，APH和aph是两个不同的变量</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">若a和b类型相同.在执行了赋值表达式a＝b后b中的值将放入a 中，而b中的值不变。</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">当从键盘输入数据时，对于整型变量只能输入整型数值,对于实型	变量只能输入实型数值。</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-09 22:05:03');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209220533', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下正确的叙述是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">在C程序中，每行中只能写一条语句</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">若a是实型变量,C程序中允许赋值a＝10，因此实型变量中允许	存放整型数</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">在C程序中,无论是整数还是实数，都能被准确无误地表示</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">在C程序中,%是只能用于整数运算的运算符</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-09 22:05:33');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209220602', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下符合C语言语法的赋值表达式是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">d＝9＋e＋f＝d＋9</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">d＝9＋e,f＝d＋9</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">d＝9＋e,e＋＋,d＋9</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">d＝9＋e＋＋＝d＋7</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-09 22:06:02');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209220647', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>已知字母A的ASCII码为十进制数65，且c2为字符型，则执行语句c2＝\'A\'＋\'6\'－\'3\';后,c2中的值为。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">D</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">68</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">不确定的值</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">C</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-09 22:06:47');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209220723', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>在C语言中，int、char和short三种类型数据在内存中所占用的字节数。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">由用户自己定义</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">均为2个字节</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">是任意的	</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">由所用机器的机器字长决定</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-09 22:07:23');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209220746', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>若有说明语句:charc＝‘\\72’;则变量c。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">包含1个字符</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">包含2个字符</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">包含3个字符</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">明不合法，c的值不确定</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-09 22:07:46');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209220817', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>若有定义:inta＝7;floatx＝2.5,y＝4.7;则表达式x＋a%3*(int)(x＋y)%2/4的值是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">2.500000	</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">2.750000	</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">3.500000</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">0.000000</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-09 22:08:17');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209220857', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>sizeof(float)是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">一个双精度型表达式</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">一个整型表达式</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">一种函数调用</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">一个不合法的表达式</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-09 22:08:57');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209220939', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>若有代数式<img class=\"fr-fin\" data-fr-image-preview=\"false\" alt=\"Image title\" src=\"img/q_img/20190211213831uploadq2.png\" width=\"90\">,则正确的C语言表达式是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">sqrt	(fabs (pow(y,x)＋log(y)))</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">sqrt	(abs	(pow(y,x)＋log(y)))</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">sqrt	(fabs (pow(x,y)＋log(y)))</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">sqrt	(abs	(pow(x,y)＋log(y)))</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-11 21:38:34');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209221049', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>设变量n为float类型,m为int类型,则以下能实现将n中的数值保留小数点后两位,第三位进行四舍五入运算的表达式是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">n＝(n*100＋0.5)/100.0</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">m＝n*100＋0.5，n＝m/100.0</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">n＝n*100＋0.5/100.0</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">n＝(n/100＋0.5)*100.0</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-09 22:10:49');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209221209', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>设以下变量均为int类型,则值不等于7的表达式是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(x＝y＝6,x＋y,x＋1)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(x＝y＝6,x＋y,y＋1)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(x＝6,x＋1,y＝6,x＋y)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(y＝6,y＋1,x＝y,x＋1)</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-09 22:12:09');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209224203', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>putchar函数可以向终端输出一个</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">整型变量表达式值</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">实型变量值</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">字符串</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">字符或字符型变量值</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-09 22:42:03');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209224624', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>已有定义inta＝－2;和输出语句：printf(\"%8lx\",a);以下正确的叙述是</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">整型变量的输出格式符只有%d一种</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">%x是格式符的一种,它可以适用于任何一种类型的数据</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">%x是格式符的一种,其变量的值按十六进制输出,但%8lx是错误的</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">%81x不是错误的格式符,其中数字8规定了输出字段的宽度</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-09 22:46:24');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209225033', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下C程序正确的运行结果是。</p><p>main(){</p><p>inty＝2456;</p><p>printf(\"y＝%3o\\n\",y);</p><p>printf(\"y＝%8o\\n\",y);</p><p>printf(\"y＝%＃8o\\n\",y);</p><p>}</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">y＝2456 y＝2456 y＝＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃2456</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">y＝4630 y＝4630 y＝＃＃＃＃＃＃＃＃4630</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">y＝2456 y＝2456 y＝02456</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">y＝4630 y＝4630 y＝04630</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-09 22:50:33');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209225122', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>若x,y均定义为int型，z定义为double型，以下不合法的scanf函数调用语句是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%d%lx,%le\",&x,&y,&z);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%2d*%d%lf\",&x,&y,&z);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%x%*d%o\",&x,&y);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%x%o%6.2f\",&x,&y,&z);</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-09 22:51:22');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209225202', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>已有如下定义和输入语句,若要求a1,a2,c1,c2的值分别为10,20,A和B,当从第一列开始输入数据时,正确的数据输入方式是。</p><p>inta1,a2;charc1,c2;</p><p>scanf(\"%d%c%d%c\",&a1,&c1,&a2,&c2);</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">10A空格20B<CR></span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">10空格A空格20空格B<CR></span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">10A20B<CR></span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">10A20空格B<CR></span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-09 22:52:02');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209225242', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>已有如下定义和输入语句,若要求a1,a2,c1,c2的值分别为10,20,A和B,当从第一列开始输入数据时,正确的数据输入方式是。</p><p>inta1,a2;charc1,c2;</p><p>scanf(\"%d%d\",&a1,&a2);</p><p>scanf(\"%c%c\",&c1,&c2);</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">1020AB<CR></span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">10空格20<CR>AB<CR></span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">10空格空格20空格空格AB<CR></span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">10空格20AB<CR></span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-09 22:52:42');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209225339', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>已有程序段和输入数据的形式如下，程序中输入语句的正确形式应当为。</p><p>main(){</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int a ; float f ;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;printf(\"\\nInputnumber:\");</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;输入语句</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;printf(\"\\nf＝%f,a＝%d\\n\",f,a);</p><p>}</p><p>Inputnumber:4.52&lt;CR&gt;</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%d,%f\",&a,&f);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%f,%d\",&f,&a);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%d%f\",&a,&f);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%f%d\",&f,&a);</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-09 22:53:39');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209225458', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>根据定义和数据的输入方式,输入语句的正确形式为。</p><p>已有定义: float f1，f2;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;数据的输入方式: 4.52&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;3.5</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%f,%f\",&f1,&f2);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%ff%f\",&f1,&f2);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%3.2f%2.1f\",&f1,&f2);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%3.2f%2.1f\",&f1,&f2);</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-10 17:26:48');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190209225833', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>阅读以下程序,当输入数据的形式为25,13,10正确的输出结果为。</p><p>main(){</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int&nbsp;x , y , z ;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;scanf(\"%d%d%d\",&x,&y,&z);</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;printf(\"x＋y＋z＝%d\\n\",x＋y＋z);</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x＋y＋z＝48</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x＋y＋z＝35</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x＋z＝35</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">不确定值</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-09 23:00:19');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210173350', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>阅读以下程序,若运行结果为如下形式,输入输出语句的正确内容是。</p><p>main(){</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int x ; float y ;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;printf( \"enterx,y:\"&nbsp;)</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;输入语句</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;输出语句</p><p>}</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;输入形式enterx,y:23.4</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;输出形式x＋y＝5.40</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%d,%f”,&x,&y);\r\nprintf(\"\\nx＋y＝%4.2f\",x＋y);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%d%f\",&x,&y);\r\nprintf(\"\\nx＋y＝%4.2f\",x＋y);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%d%f\",&x,&y);\r\nprintf(\"\\nx＋y＝%6.1f\",x＋y);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%d%3.1f\",&x,&y);\r\nprintf(\"\\nx＋y＝%4.2f\",x＋y);</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-10 17:33:50');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210173431', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下说法正确的是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">输入项可以为一实型常最,如scanf(\"%f\",3.5);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">只有格式控制，没有输入项，也能进行正确输入，如scanf(\"a＝%d,b＝%d\");</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">当输人一个实型数据时，格式控制部分应规定小数点后的位数,如scanf(\"%4.2f\",&f);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">当输入数据时,必须指明变量的地址,如scanf(\"%f\",&f);</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-10 17:34:31');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210173551', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>根据下面的程序及数据的输入方式和输出形式，程序中输入语句的正确形式应该为。</p><p>main(){</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;char ch1,ch2,ch3;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;输入语句</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;printf(\"%c%c%c”,ch1,ch2,cb3);</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;}</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;输入形式:ABC</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;输出形式:AB</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%c%c%c\",&ch1,&ch2,&ch3);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%c,%c,%c\",&ch1,&ch2,&ch3);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%c%c%c\",&ch1,&ch2,&ch3);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">scanf(\"%c%c\",&ch1,&ch2,&ch3);</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-10 17:35:51');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210173619', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>有输入语句：scanf(\"a＝%d,b＝%d,c＝%d\",&a,&b,&c);为使变量a的值为1,b为3,c为2,从键盘输入数据的正确形式应当是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">132<回车></span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">1,3,2<回车></span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">a＝1b＝3c＝2<回车></span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">a＝1,b＝3,c＝2<回车></span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-10 17:36:19');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210173647', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下能正确地定义整型变量a,b和c并为其赋初值5的语句是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">int a＝b＝c＝5;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">int a,b,c＝5;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">a＝5,b＝5,c＝5;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">a＝b＝c＝5;</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-10 17:36:47');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210173714', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>已知ch是字符型变量,下面不正确的赋值语句是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">ch＝\'a＋b\';	</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">ch＝\'\\0\';</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">ch＝\'7\'＋\'9\';</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">ch＝5＋9;</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-10 17:37:14');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210173751', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>已知ch是字符型变量,下面正确的赋值语句是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">ch＝\'123\';</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">ch＝\'\\xff\';	</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">ch＝\'\\08\';</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">ch＝\"\\\";</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-10 17:37:51');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210190745', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>若有以下定义，则正确的赋值语句是。</p><p>int a,b; float x;</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">a＝1,b＝2,</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">b＋＋;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">a＝b＝5;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">b＝int(x);</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-10 19:07:45');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210190815', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>设x、y均为float型变量，则以下不合法的赋值语句是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">＋＋x;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">y＝(x%2)/10;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x*＝y＋8;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x＝y＝0;</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-10 19:08:15');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210190949', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>没x、y和z均为int型变量,则执行语句x＝(y＝(z＝10)＋5)－5;后,x、y和z的值是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x＝10;\r\ny＝15;\r\nz＝10;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x＝10;\r\nz＝10;\r\ny=10;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x=10;\r\ny=10;\r\nz=15;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x=10;\r\ny=5;\r\nz=10</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-10 19:09:49');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210191030', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>设有说明:doubley＝0.5，z＝1.5;intx＝10;则能够正确使用C语言库函数的赋值语句是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">z＝exp(y)＋fabs(x)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">y＝log10(y)＋pow(y)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">z＝sqrt(y－z)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x＝(int)(atan2((double)x,y)＋exp(y－0.2))</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-10 19:10:30');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210194254', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>逻辑运算符两侧运算对象的数据据类型</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">只能是0或1</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">只能是0或非0正数</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">只能是整型或字符型数据</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">可以是任何类型的数据</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-10 19:42:54');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210194327', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下关于运算符优先顺序的描述中正确的是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">关系运算符<算术运算符<赋值运算符<逻辑与运算符</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">逻辑与运算符<关系运算符<算术运算符<赋值运算符</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">赋值运算符<逻辑与运算符<关系运算符<算术运算符</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">算术运算符<关系运算符<赋值运算符<逻辑与运算符</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-10 19:43:28');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210194356', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>下列运算符中优先级最高的是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\"><</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">＋</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">&&</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">!＝</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-10 19:43:56');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210194421', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>能正确表示“当x的取值在[1,10]和[200,210]范围内为真，否则为假”的表达式是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(x>＝1)&&(x<＝10)&&(x>＝200)&&(x<＝210)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(x>＝1)||(x<＝10)||(x>＝200)||(x<＝210)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(x>＝1)&&(x<＝10)||(x>＝200)&&(x<＝210)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(x>＝1)||(x<＝10)&&(x>＝200)||(x<＝210)</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-10 19:44:21');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190210194506', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>表示图中坐标轴上阴影部分的正确表达式是。</p><p><br><img class=\"fr-fin\" data-fr-image-preview=\"false\" alt=\"Image title\" src=\"img/q_img/20190211194232uploadq_106.png\" width=\"300\"></p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(x<＝a)&&(x>＝b)&&(x<＝c)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(x<＝a)||(b<＝x<＝c)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(x<＝a)||(x>＝b)&&(x<＝c)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(x<＝a)&&(b<＝x<＝c)</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-11 19:43:19');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211203957', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>判断char型变量ch是否为大写字母的正确表达式是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">\'A\'<＝ch<＝\'Z\'</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(ch>＝\'A\')&(ch<＝\'Z\')</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(ch>＝\'A\')&&(ch<＝\'Z\')</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(\'A\'<＝ch)AND(\'Z\'>＝ch)</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-11 20:39:57');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204024', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>设x、y和z是int型变量,且x＝3,y＝4,z＝5，则下面表达式中值为0的是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">\'x\'&&\'y\'</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x<＝y</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x||y＋z&&y－z</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">!((x<y)&&!z||1)</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-11 20:40:24');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204048', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>已知x＝43,ch＝\'A\',y＝0;则表达式(x&gt;＝y&&ch&lt;\'B\'&&!y)的值是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">0</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">语法错</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">1</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">“假”</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-11 20:40:48');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204115', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>若希望当A的值为奇数时,表达式的值为“真”，A的值为偶数时,表达式的值为“假”。则以下不能满足要求的表达式是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">A%2＝＝1</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">!(A%2＝＝0)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">!(A%2)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">A%2</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-11 20:41:15');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204140', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>设有:inta＝1,b＝2,c＝3,d＝4,m＝2,n＝2;执行(m＝a&gt;b)&&(n＝c&gt;d)后n的值为。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">1</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">2</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">3</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">4</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-11 20:41:40');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204204', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>判断char型变量c1是否为小写字母的正确表达式为。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">\'a\'<＝c1<＝\'z\'</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(c1>＝a)&&(cl<＝z)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(\'a\'>＝cl)||(\'z\'<＝c1)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(c1>＝\'a\')&&(c1<＝\'z\')</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-11 20:42:04');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204241', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下程序的运行结果是。</p><p>＃include\"stdio.h\"</p><p>main(){</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int a,b,d＝241;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a＝d/100%9;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;b＝(－1)&&(－1);</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;printf(\"%d,%d\",a,b);</p><p>}</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">6,1</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">2,1</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">6,0</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">2,0</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-11 20:42:41');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204357', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下不正确的if语句形式是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x>y&&x!＝y);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x＝＝y)x＋＝y;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x!＝y)scanf(\"%d\",&x)elsescanf(\"%d\",&y);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x<y){x＋＋;y＋＋;}</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-11 20:43:57');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204428', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>已知intx＝l0,y＝20,z＝30;以下语句执行后x,y,z的值是。</p><p>if(x&gt;y)</p><p>z＝x;x＝y;y＝z;</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x＝10,y＝20,z＝30</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x＝20,y＝30,z＝30</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x＝20,y＝30,z＝10</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">x＝20,y＝30,z＝20</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-11 20:44:28');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204456', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下if语句语法正确的是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x>0)\r\nprintf(\"%f\",x)\r\nelse\r\nprintf(\"%f\",－x);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x>0)\r\n{x＝x＋y;printf(\"%f\",x);}\r\nelse\r\nprintf(\"%f\",－x);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x>0)\r\n{x＝x＋y;printf(\"%f\",x);};\r\nelse\r\nprintf(\"%f\",－x);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x>0)\r\n		{x＝x＋y;printf(\"%f\",x)}\r\nelse\r\nprintf(\"%f\",－x);</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-11 20:45:20');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204603', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>请阅读以下程序:</p><p>main(){</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int a＝5,b＝0,c＝0;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(a＝b＋c)printf(\"***\\n\");</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else			printf(\"$$$\\n\");</p><p>}</p><p>以上程序。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">有语法错不能通过编译</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">可以通过编译但不能通过连接</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">输出***</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">输出$$$</span></span></div>', 'D', '2019-02-11 20:46:03');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204625', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下程序的运行结果是。</p><p>main(){</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int m＝5;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(m＋＋&gt;5)printf(\"%d\\n\",m);</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else		printf(\"%d\\n\",m－－);</p><p>}</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">4</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">5</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">6</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">7</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-11 20:46:25');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204642', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>当a＝1,b－3,c＝5.d＝4时,执行完下面一段程序后x的值是。</p><p>if(a&lt;b)</p><p>if(c&lt;d&gt;x＝1</p><p>else</p><p>if(a&lt;c)</p><p>if(b&lt;d)x＝2;</p><p>elsex＝3;</p><p>elsex＝6;</p><p>elsex＝7;</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">1</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">2</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">3</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">6</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-11 20:46:42');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204920', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下程序的输出结果是。</p><p>main(){</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int a＝100,x＝10,y＝20,ok1＝5,ok2＝0;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(x&lt;y)</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(y!＝10)</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(!ok1)</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a＝1;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;else</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;if(ok2)a＝10;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;a＝－1;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;printf(\"%d\\n\",a);</p><p>}</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">1</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">0</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">-1</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">值不确定</span></span></div>', 'C', '2019-02-11 20:49:20');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211204943', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下程序的输出结果是。</p><p>main()</p><p>{intx＝2,y＝－1,z＝2;</p><p>if(x&lt;y)</p><p>if(y&lt;0)z＝0;</p><p>elsez＋＝1;</p><p>printf(\"%d\\n\",z);</p><p>}</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">3</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">2</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">1</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">0</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-11 20:49:43');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211205024', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>为了避免在嵌套的条件语句if－else中产生二义性,C语言规定:else子句总是与配对。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">缩排位置相同的if</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">其之前最近的if</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">其之后最近的if</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">同一行上的if</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-11 20:50:24');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211205052', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>以下不正确的语句为。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x>y);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x＝y)&&(x!＝0)x＋＝y;</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x!＝y)scanf(\"%d\",&x);elsescanf(\"%d\",&y);</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">if(x<y){x＋＋;y＋＋;}</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-11 20:50:52');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211205144', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>若有条件表达式(exp)?a＋＋:b－－,则以下表达式中能完全等价于表达式(exp)的是。</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(exp＝＝0)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(exp!＝0)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(exp＝＝1)</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">(exp!＝1)</span></span></div>', 'B', '2019-02-11 20:51:44');
INSERT INTO `question` VALUES ('120190211205213', '单选题', 3, 'C语言', '<div class=\"exam-q\"><p>若运行时给变量x输入12,则以下程序的运行结果是。</p><p>main(){</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;int x,y;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;scanf(\"%d\",&x);</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;y＝x&gt;12?x＋10:x－12;</p><p>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;printf(\"%d\\n\",y);</p><p>}</p></div><div class=\"exam-o\"><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">A、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">0</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">B、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">22</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">C、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">12</span></span><span class=\"op\"><span class=\"op-item\">D、</span><span class=\"op-answer\">10</span></span></div>', 'A', '2019-02-11 20:52:13');
